<div style="width:0;height:0;clear:both"></div><dl class="lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle-">
<dd class="lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle-title">
<h1>艺术形式</h1>
<h2>（对艺术形式的解释）</h2>
<a class="edit-lemma cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-edit-link" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="lock-lemma" href="javascript:;" nslog-type="10003105" target="_blank" title="锁定"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_lock-lemma"></em>锁定</a>
<a class="lemma-discussion cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-discussion-link" href="/planet/talk?lemmaId=1425273" nslog-type="90000102" target="_blank"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_discussion-solid"></em>讨论<span class="num">999</span></a>
</dd>
</dl><div class="promotion-declaration">
</div><div class="lemma-summary" label-module="lemmaSummary">
<div class="para" label-module="para">形式是指<a data-lemmaid="1693084" href="/item/%E4%BA%8B%E7%89%A9/1693084" target="_blank">事物</a>和现象的内容要素的组织构造和外在形式。艺术形式与<a href="/item/%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9" target="_blank">艺术内容</a>并举，指的是艺术作品内部的组织构造和外在的<a data-lemmaid="7489936" href="/item/%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81/7489936" target="_blank">表现形态</a>以及种种艺术手段的<a data-lemmaid="35024" href="/item/%E6%80%BB%E5%92%8C/35024" target="_blank">总和</a>。</div>
</div>
<div class="configModuleBanner">
</div><div class="basic-info cmn-clearfix">
<dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-left">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">中文名</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
艺术形式
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">外文名</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
form in art
</dd>
</dl><dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-right">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">形式内容</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
内形式，外形式
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">关    系</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
相对独立
</dd>
</dl></div>
